# Title: Diagnostic Library Sdiageng.DLL Loaded By Msdt.EXE
# Author: Greg (rule)
# Date: 2022-06-17
# Level: high
# Description: Detects both of CVE-2022-30190 (Follina) and DogWalk vulnerabilities exploiting msdt.exe binary to load the "sdiageng.dll" library
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1202, cve.2022-30190
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_dll_sdiageng_load_by_msdt.yml

ImageLoaded="*\\sdiageng.dll" Image="*\\msdt.exe"